<Base title="Conversation menu - vals.quest">
  <h1>Conversation menu</h1>
  <p><em>This was written 2023/2024 and is somewhat outdated, with a bunch of my interests growing in the meditation, enlightenment and solving psychological problems direction, + forecasting and many others. This list is not exhaustive, I enjoy many more things still.</em></p>

  <p>Things I might wanna talk about, among many not listed here:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Ethics</li>
    <li>Psychology, Psychiatry</li>
    <li>Therapy, Self improvement, Group improvement</li>
    <li>Meditation theory, phenomenology</li>
    <li>Well-being and productivity</li>
    <li>Refining models of
      <ul>
        <li>General Intelligence, limits of optimization</li>
        <li>Is knowing how to reliably do "intelligence improvement" all one needs to be general? Hill climbing? How robust must your hill climbing be?</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Game theory, Games, Game Design, Economy</li>
    <li>Society</li>
    <li>Meaning and Values, Fun</li>
    <li>Philosophy</li>
    <li>Modelling the probability of x-risks, notably AI x-risks
      <ul>
        <li>Modelling best paths to reduce these</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr />

  <h2>And yours</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your work</li>
    <li>Your life</li>
    <li>Your philosophy</li>
    <li>Your hopes and dreams</li>
    <li>Your frustrations, difficulties, problems</li>
  </ul>
</Base>
